<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Confirmation - ELearning</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #4f5ef1;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .message-sm {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 50px;
    }

    .message-sm h1 {
      font-size: 25px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .course-info {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #000000;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .course-info h4 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #23bd70;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .order-details {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #0000002f;
    }

    .order-details td {
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .order-details .first-td {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #0000006c;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .order-details .second-td {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #000000af;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .table-row {
      border-top: 1px solid #00000029;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }

    .table-row td {
      padding: 10px 0;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
  </head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="message-sm">
      <h1>Your ELearning Order is Confirmed!</h1>
      <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
      </div>
    <div class="course-info">
      <h4>Here's What You Ordered:</h4>
      <table class="order-details">
        <tr>
          <td class="first-td">Order #:</td>
          <td class="second-td">
            <%= order._id %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="first-td">Order Date:</td>
          <td class="second-td">
            <%= order.date %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        </table>
      <table class="order-details">
        <tr>
          <td class="first-td">Item</td>
          <td class="first-td">Qty</td>
          <td class="first-td">Cost</td>
          </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="second-td">
            <%= order.name %>
          </td>
          <td class="second-td">1</td>
          <td class="second-td">$<%= order.price %>
          </td>
          </tr>
          </table>
      <table class="table-row">
        <tr>
          <td>Subtotal:</td>
          <td>$<%= order.price %>
          </td>
          </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Total:</td>
          <td>$<%= order.price %>
          </td>
          </tr>
          </table>
          </div>
          <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a
          href="mailto:support@eduhub.co.ke">support@eduhub.co.ke</a></p>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> EduHub. All rights reserved.</p>
      
      </div>
      </div>
      </body>

</html>